==召回==
2020年6月，因為碳積累導致引擎顫動問題，捷恩斯暫停柴油版GV80的交付<ref>{{cite news|last1=Herald|first1=The Korea|date=5 June 2020|title=Hyundai delays delivery of GV80 SUV following engine vibration issue|language=en|work=The Korea Herald|url=http://m.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20200605000654|accessdate=31 October 2020|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107084616/http://m.koreaherald.com/view.php?ud=20200605000654|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同年9月，8,783輛GV80因為引擎失速問題被召回<ref name="GV80 diesel">{{cite news|date=6 October 2020|title=GV80 diesel becomes headache for Hyundai Motor|work=The Korea Times|url=http://m.koreatimes.co.kr/pages/article.asp?newsIdx=297127|accessdate=31 October 2020|archive-date=2020-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201103111549/http://m.koreatimes.co.kr/pages/article.asp?newsIdx=297127|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

